---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cookie Policy — AgentleConsulting"
  description="AgentleConsulting Cookie Policy. How we use cookies and your choices regarding tracking.">

  <div class="bg-cream py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="container-site max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="font-heading font-bold text-4xl text-slate mb-2">Cookie Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate/50 mb-12">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-slate/75 space-y-8">
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">What Are Cookies?</h2>
          <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help websites remember your preferences and understand how you use the site.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">Cookies We Use</h2>
          <p><strong>Functional Cookie:</strong> We use one functional cookie to remember your cookie consent preference. This cookie expires after 12 months.</p>
          <p><strong>Analytics (with consent):</strong> If you click "Accept All," we use Google Analytics to understand aggregate website traffic patterns. This data is anonymized and helps us improve the site.</p>
          <p>We do not use advertising cookies or tracking pixels.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">Your Choices</h2>
          <p>When you first visit our site, you'll see a cookie consent banner. You can:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Accept All:</strong> Enables analytics tracking and stores your preference</li>
            <li><strong>Reject:</strong> Only the functional consent cookie is set; no analytics</li>
            <li><strong>Cookie Policy link:</strong> Read this policy before deciding</li>
          </ul>
          <p>You can withdraw consent at any time by clearing your cookies or emailing us.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">Third-Party Cookies</h2>
          <p><strong>Calendly:</strong> If you book a call via our Calendly embed, Calendly may set its own cookies. See their <a href="https://calendly.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sage">Cookie Policy</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">Contact</h2>
          <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:hello@agentleconsulting.com" class="text-sage">hello@agentleconsulting.com</a>.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
